"Frequently. weight: 12 aliases: - /help/faq —"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/about/contribute/front-matter/index.rst:88
msgid ""
"The change above allows any user to access the FAQ when they visit "
"``https://istio.io/faq/`` or ``https://istio.io/help/faq/``."
msgstr ""

